# <type>(<scope>): <subject>  ← keep under 72 chars
#
# Types: feat | fix | refactor | test | docs | chore | ci | perf | style
#
# Common scopes for this project:
#   api        → apps/api (NestJS backend)
#   web        → apps/web (Next.js frontend)
#   auth       → auth wiring, guards, decorators
#   dashboard  → apps/web/app/dashboard/**
#   platform   → platform admin area
#   prisma     → schema, migrations, seed
#   infra      → Docker, Redis, config modules
#   ws         → WebSocket gateway / client
#   deps       → dependency updates
#
# Body (optional — wrap at 72 chars):
#   Explain WHY, not what. The diff already shows what changed.
#   Reference Matrix rows when a feature lands: "Covers FCM #8, #10."
#
# Co-authored-by line (add when AI assisted):
# Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
#
# Examples:
#   feat(dashboard): add MFA setup + recovery codes modal
#   fix(api): scope invitation list query by tenantId
#   refactor(auth): extract scrypt helpers into account.service
#   test(api): add e2e spec for session FIFO eviction
#
# NEVER commit:
#   - .env files or secrets
#   - node_modules, dist, .next, coverage
#   - console.log / @ts-ignore / eslint-disable left in source
